descriptionHtml:
Passbook is banking for immigrants. No long lines. No unfair fees. No SSN required if you don’t have one. Launching 2020. Join the waitlist today.

Remitly changed the way you send money. Now we will change the way you save and spend.

CHANGING BANKING ONE FEE AT A TIME
No maintenance fees. No overdraft fees. No minimum balance fees. No fees at select ATMs.

TRAVEL WITH YOUR PASSBOOK
The Passbook Visa® Debit Card can be used everywhere Visa debit cards are accepted. We don’t charge foreign transaction fees. Access 1.8M ATMs worldwide. Enable and disable your Visa Debit card in the app to help prevent unauthorized charges.

MAKE IT YOUR FIRST BANK ACCOUNT
You can sign up for Passbook even before you get an SSN, once you have a physical US address. We accept ITIN, passports, and other foreign government-issued IDs if you don’t have an SSN.

CHOOSE YOUR FLAG
Sign up today and receive a beautiful Passbook Visa debit card with your country flag on it.

SEND WITH REMITLY, GET CASH BACK
When you send money internationally with Remitly and use your Passbook Visa Debit card to pay, get $2 cash back for every transfer.

---

Goodbye paying unfair fees
Goodbye “US citizens only”
Goodbye 3-5 days to send money
Goodbye having to visit a branch or agent

Hello modern banking for immigrants
Hello doing everything from your mobile phone
Hello beautiful Visa card with your country flag on it

Hello Passbook

---

title: Passbook by Remitly

creator: Remitly
descriptionHtml:
Introducing Passbook by Remitly, banking designed for immigrants first. Remitly changed the way you send money. Now we will change the way you bank and spend.

NO FEES → save money by not paying any banking, membership, or maintenance fees.

SSN not required → if you don’t have a Social Security Number, we can verify your identity using passport or Mexican Matricula Consular.

FDIC insured → your money is insured by the FDIC, up to $250,000.

Get a beautiful Visa® debit card → with your country flag on it.

Use while traveling → the Passbook Visa debit card can be used everywhere Visa debit cards are accepted, without foreign transaction fees or hiked up exchange rates.

$2 cash back → when you send money internationally using Remitly and use your Passbook Visa debit card as the payment method.

Mobile banking via app → check your balance and get real-time transaction notifications from your smartphone. Plus, use your phone to pay with Apple Pay® or Google Pay®!

Deposit cash at stores → use stores like Walmart and Walgreens to deposit cash. Almost 90k store locations supported.

Amazing customer service → dedicated specialists, available via email or phone. Hablamos Español.

By Remitly → we’ve helped millions of immigrants send billions of dollars to their friends and families.


===

Apple Pay is a registered trademark of Apple Inc. and is registered in the U.S. and other countries.

Google Pay is a registered trademark of Google LLC.

title: Passbook by Remitly

creator: Remitly
descriptionHtml:
Introducing Passbook by Remitly, the bank account for multi-nationals. Remitly changed the way you send money internationally. Now we will change the way you bank and spend.

NO FEES → save money by not paying any banking, membership, or maintenance fees.

SSN not required → if you don’t have a Social Security Number, we can verify your identity using passport or Mexican Matricula Consular.

FDIC insured → your money is insured by the FDIC, up to $250,000.

Get a beautiful Visa® debit card → with your country flag on it.

Use while traveling → the Passbook Visa debit card can be used everywhere Visa debit cards are accepted, without foreign transaction fees or hiked up exchange rates.

$2 cash back → when you send money internationally using Remitly and use your Passbook Visa debit card as the payment method.

Mobile banking via app → check your balance and get real-time transaction notifications from your smartphone. Plus, use your phone to pay with Google Pay®!

Deposit cash at stores → use stores like Walmart and Walgreens to deposit cash. Almost 90k store locations supported.

Amazing customer service → dedicated specialists, available via email or phone. Hablamos Español.

By Remitly → we’ve helped millions of immigrants send billions of dollars to their friends and families.


===

The Passbook Visa debit card is issued by Sunrise Banks N.A., Member FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa U.S.A. Inc. The card can be used everywhere Visa debit cards are accepted. Use of the card constitutes acceptance of the terms and conditions stated in the Account Agreement.

Google Pay is a registered trademark of Google LLC.

title: Passbook by Remitly

creator: Remitly
descriptionHtml:
Passbook is an everyday banking account with no foreign transaction fees, cash back on international transfers, early payday, and a beautiful Visa® debit card with your choice of flag.

(The Passbook app is by Remitly, a financial technology company. Banking services are provided by Sunrise Banks, N.A.; Member FDIC)

→ Goodbye, fees
Save money by not paying any banking, membership, or maintenance fees.

→ Swipe with pride
Get a beautiful Visa debit card with your country flag and preferred name on it.

→ Designed for you, by Remitly
Since 2011, we’ve helped millions of immigrants send billions of dollars to their friends and family.

→ Banking without borders
Use internationally without foreign transaction fees, everywhere Visa® debit cards are accepted.

→ Peace of mind
Passbook accounts are insured by the FDIC up to $250,000.

→ Get cash back
Get $2 back when you send money internationally using Remitly and use your Passbook Visa debit card as the payment method.

→ Get paid early
Set up direct deposit to your Passbook account and we’ll make the money available up to two days early.*

→ Deposit when and where you want
Use stores like Walmart and Walgreens to deposit cash. Almost 90k store locations supported.

→ Smarter spending
Get real-time spending notifications on your smartphone and use your phone to pay with Apple Pay®

→ Get help when you need it
Dedicated specialists, available internationally even outside banking hours via email or phone.


===

The Passbook app is by Remitly, a financial technology company. Banking services are provided by Sunrise Banks N.A. The Passbook Visa® debit card is issued by Sunrise Banks N.A., Member FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa U.S.A. Inc. The card can be used everywhere Visa debit cards are accepted.

title: Passbook by Remitly

creator: Remitly
descriptionHtml:
Passbook is brought to you by the same company that created Remitly, the app that millions of customers trust to send money internationally. Sign up in minutes to get a mobile account and Visa® debit card. No minimum deposits or fees, even when spending internationally. No SSN required, and no checks on credit history or immigration status.¹

Deposit cash to your Passbook account at 90K retail stores nationwide,² or transfer funds from a bank, PayPal®, Venmo, Cash App or Zelle®. Spend everywhere Visa debit cards are accepted. Get cash back when spending at major retailers, and withdraw cash fee-free from thousands of ATMs in the Plus® Alliance network. Plus, save $2 on Remitly international money transfers.³

Benefits:
➔ NO FEES: No minimum balances or fees — not even for foreign transactions
➔ EASY CASH DEPOSITS: Deposit at major retailers including Walmart, 7-Eleven, Dollar General, Dollar Tree, CVS, Walgreens, Rite Aid, Kroger, and Safeway
➔ EASY CASH WITHDRAWALS: Withdraw from 2 million ATMs worldwide, or get cash back when spending at most major retailers, grocery stores, and drug stores
➔ SPEND AROUND THE WORLD: Spend everywhere Visa debit cards are accepted, with no foreign transaction fees
➔ SEND AROUND THE WORLD: Get $2 cash back on Remitly international money transfers. Send to other U.S. Passbook account holders, in minutes and for free⁴
➔ EARLY PAYDAY: Get your paycheck up to 2 days early when you set up direct deposit⁵
